  "texts": [
    "Continued investigation is essential to integrate radiogenomics data effectively into clinical practice and decision-making.",
    "Immunological modulatorSince the immune system plays a critical role in RPT, our TDT models can be improved using an immunological modulator.",
    "This module will add immunological factors, such as tumor microenvironment, immunological cell death, antigen, and cytokine expression on the TDT models to improve and personalize the model.",
    "These immune factors can be obtained using lab tests or other measurements.The tumor microenvironment is a complex system that involves a variety of immune cells, growth factors, and cytokines.",
    "Understanding the specific characteristics of a patient's tumor microenvironment can help predict their response to different therapies."
  ],
